title: Anne Rice - The Mummy
description:
Anne Rice 
              - The Mummy or Ramses The Damned -
		        [Audiobook]
 
Anne Rice weaves the same magic for the world and history of mummies that she 
previously did for the worlds and mythologies of vampires and witches. 
Ramses the Great lives, but having drunk the elixir of life, he is now 
Ramses the Damned, doomed forever to wander the earth, desperate to quell 
certain mummy hungers that can never be satisfied!
